'''Caleb Gravesend''' (1982-April 10th, 2068) was a British firefighter.

== Early life and education ==
Caleb Gravesend was born to Rod Gravesend and Scarlett Woodbridge in 1982.

He attended primary school from 1987 to 1993 and secondary school from 1993 to 2000.

== Career ==
Caleb Gravesend started a new position as Probationary Firefighter for Swansea Fire Department in 2001 and was eventually laid-off from the job in 2035. However, he was hired for the same job at the same department the same year, but was laid-off again in 2037.{{Infobox character|name=Caleb Gravesend|relatives=[[Rod Gravesend]] (father)
